rows.label: qst104709_msg001
rows.name: Leave the grounded ship to me.

rows.label: qst104709_msg002
rows.name:
I have a favor to ask, so
let's meet up in Gula.

rows.label: qst104709_msg0001
rows.name:
My husband and the others went
with the Blade through the Cloudway
right over there to get help.

rows.label: qst104709_msg0002
rows.name:
She didn't have her Driver, so
I advised her to stay with us,
but she wouldn't listen...

rows.label: qst104709_msg0101
rows.name:
My husband and the others are
safe! Oh, thank goodness...

rows.label: qst104709_msg0102
rows.name:
I'll prepare so that they're
ready whenever they come back!
